{"tid":1535210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(新三不戰略)！不留到夜晚！不圍警署！不到人少地方！","createTime":"2019-09-03T09:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T12:31:06.000Z","uid":50457,"like":111,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d6309a0c4b2bf388f6cb5fe389b2f55dc062b8","tid":1535210,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:26:30.000Z","msg":"利申：終極和理非，不建議任何違法行為<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">不留到夜晚</span><br />\n<br />\n冬令將至，日落時間會提早，所有活動盡量日落前完。過去1100多人被捕，其中超過80%都係晚上拘捕的。原因一：街上路人減少，即掩護的人減少，令到抗爭者直接暴露於黑警面前。<br />\n<br />\n星期一至五，有返工／放工的人群掩護，港鐵封站機會比較細，因為一封站全港交通大亂，黑警要增援亦極困難。但市民支援更易，要深夜叫人支援極困難。<br />\n<br />\n星期六，日風險較高，因為沒有返工群眾，但好處係聚集到的人群較多，場面亦較大規模。<br />\n<br />\n日落後繼續聚集，風險極高。原因: 黨鐵會即時停，公路亦即時終斷，視線變暗，黑警更容易私刑同時無辦法清楚拍攝，逃走變得極困難，同時大部分群眾已散去令到餘下人士更危險。<br />\n<br />\n早上大家未瞓醒，亦無咁易上力，或暴躁，同理用於黑警，早上黑警暴力無咁痛，夜晚就好痛。日落後仲想留低，真係諗清諗楚！！！<br />\n<br />\n好處：未諗到<br />\n<br />\n黑警見光死，夜晚先夠膽出嚟作惡，過往3個月完全睇到係呢個情況，等同魔鬼只會夜晚作惡一樣。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">不圍警署</span><br />\n<br />\n已數唔清有幾多個手捉係警署附近被捕，同被打，仲有中槍。之前有好多人講過唔好去圍警署，在此，不厭其煩再講當中利幣。<br />\n<br />\n第一： 黑警以逸待勞<br />\n除非手捉主動衝入去(至今連行到門口都少之有少), 否則佢哋理鬼你哋出面做咩，睇住電視等你哋企4&sim;5個鐘，浪費體力同精神。<br />\n<br />\n第二：無限裝備補充<br />\n打機都要邊行邊執子彈，如果唔係會用晒。邊有人咁蠢，圍人地武器庫，黑警射完10粒催淚彈，然後行幾步入倉再攞過繼續射，你哋就係出面捱打。你諗下倒返轉，如果成隊人要坐車去第二度，攞的裝備變成有限，射一粒少一粒，射到無就要撤退或者用近身武器。8月5日點解天水圍被人拉咁多人，黃大仙反而被人反攻入警署，原因之一就係呢樣。當日圍天水圍警署，人地用幾丁友係警署射射射，你地就散晒。之後出嚟掃場，輕鬆圍捕。黃大仙當時遠離警署，變成無支援，最後接近彈藥耗盡被街坊反攻成功。<br />\n<br />\n而最重要的是，圍警署等同比對方有足夠通訊同時間搵支援反圍市民。太多次不能盡錄，基本上呢個場面一次又一次出現，送頭又送頭。<br />\n<br />\n好處：純粹地標易認，同好似圍住政權的意識表態。<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">不到人少的地方</span><br />\n如果連同抗爭者，得唔夠100人，必須要即時解散活動。原因好簡單：人少的時候混入群眾的黑警先夠膽表露身份拉人，你諗下，呢班鬼最多就一隊5&sim;10人左右，如果混入2000人裡面拉人，應該被人溶左都唔知咩事。佢哋雖然恐武有力，但1打10都唔係咁易，更可況1打50。銅鑼灣之所以第一次團滅，主因必然係到了人少的地方，而唔係到了有內鬼的地方。第二次，反而迫到黑警開兩槍實彈就知，<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>鬼唔係問題，人少先係問題。<br />\n<br />\n好處：除非真快閃，否則千萬不要參與少過100人的活動。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日大家將焦點放係唔知真定假的太子事件，不如放返精神做其他事。"},{"pid":"dd947acf39cc189638207da65818b0bbe1062866","tid":1535210,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdcd209a1d0fa2119c07e2a249e3604d5ab7c17f","tid":1535210,"uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"不要抗爭<br />\n坐定定就贏<br />\nyeah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcbe50a985d0d0517ee6355ecae16bf71ec9c05","tid":1535210,"uid":63167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdcd209a1d0fa2119c07e2a249e3604d5ab7c17f","tid":1535210,"uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"不要抗爭<br />\n坐定定就贏<br />\nyeah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:31:02.000Z","msg":"有咩問題"},{"pid":"7e5974b7ed1baaf444c45ba70da2028f5080734c","tid":1535210,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"【恐慌絕對會傳染】打算係戰場出聲/指揮，請先控制你既情緒聲線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535121</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65a6a6a809751bba52188d2d938e6dfb21c8a8ea","tid":1535210,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdcd209a1d0fa2119c07e2a249e3604d5ab7c17f","tid":1535210,"uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"不要抗爭<br />\n坐定定就贏<br />\nyeah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:33:06.000Z","msg":"【恐慌絕對會傳染】打算係戰場出聲/指揮，請先控制你既情緒聲線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535121</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc69858759837daabb866a79879ed9f9caa89cd9","tid":1535210,"uid":78850,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"岩岩放工 5點鐘 銅鑼灣黨鐵閘位有防暴狗"},{"pid":"c0bf785079564d9f8f04b97e7f5d440c06ab3cb0","tid":1535210,"uid":108133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"真心覺得要浪費體力+被補風險圍警署<br />\n不如買雞蛋掉或者小强係狗局狗宿舍放生仲好"},{"pid":"f2099da6a9fd4206e04d0b39eb8e7e28a4c649b8","tid":1535210,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crzdsEZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcrzdsEZ.jpg&h=1c47cc17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[禍必及妻兒]所有人FB/IG等等即刻轉頭像<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534795</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34421a9538628551a2670b0320b1aedcebcdb7fb","tid":1535210,"uid":277540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"仲有幾曰就8/9  我等到頸長  大家呢幾日都係要小心出入"},{"pid":"7cf799b987734aef92bc68171f13c98b7590b1ca","tid":1535210,"uid":2264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:37:30.000Z","msg":"圍狗宿會唔會好過狗屋啊"},{"pid":"87c11c7e80d9c282bdba83b66d7adeaa53f2a002","tid":1535210,"uid":192551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多"},{"pid":"28f5ff5d630491277c96c078b932dffd380c85c3","tid":1535210,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"你知唔知和理非唔係解唔犯法?<br />\n咁多人畀人拉係因為和理非未有擔當成為勇武嘅盾嘅決心﹐我指真係企嘅勇武前方擋住班狗"},{"pid":"9d32c467a36af80cf06c72294ad60e8297e209bd","tid":1535210,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:42:02.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"4a479d589d838cffe5195fa50b192cf3821377a2","tid":1535210,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87c11c7e80d9c282bdba83b66d7adeaa53f2a002","tid":1535210,"uid":192551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:42:39.000Z","msg":"已經好耐無人出策略帖"},{"pid":"af268a5378f4ec631c1ca90c5887739aab73313a","tid":1535210,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28f5ff5d630491277c96c078b932dffd380c85c3","tid":1535210,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"你知唔知和理非唔係解唔犯法?<br />\n咁多人畀人拉係因為和理非未有擔當成為勇武嘅盾嘅決心﹐我指真係企嘅勇武前方擋住班狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:46:30.000Z","msg":"你呢個係現場時唔同崗位的要求，至今都未見到系統的論述，所以需要大家更多分享。否則每次上場的經驗承傳不了，浪費好多經驗值。<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係點解，開始慢慢策略上輸比克警，係因為佢哋每次都有重估檢討。"},{"pid":"f4dd7161467acca6392c3816cc9ff863e672771b","tid":1535210,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:46:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a6a62db1124573f9d90b669c24442e64bc9b5d0","tid":1535210,"uid":54243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"219c27f9ab374c6afc042bcca6b912962d296aea","tid":1535210,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5612173d99cda38e14ce6c17149db03b721c04d","tid":1535210,"uid":278689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b112fe88a4fb65896625ddcf36dc103decf68a51","tid":1535210,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcf93ae72a17c9af326e3472879a5edbbeda0745","tid":1535210,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4af5571a3c6885ed77ed9d9516e120b8c09c943","tid":1535210,"uid":8170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"圍唔緊要，唔好搞到太夜，條街多人佢地唔會亂嚟。建議十點左右散。"},{"pid":"9a4f39c6fc2dc682251b73a64a4c2520ecda5e22","tid":1535210,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"5d719d5b162bba97aceb02d57eaae62c12ec7904","tid":1535210,"uid":223428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:15:05.000Z","msg":"同埋其實圍住警署侮辱似乎不能表達訴求"},{"pid":"907de69949082679817c118459a193439f39c143","tid":1535210,"uid":185960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:17:18.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勿亂叫要人<br />\n自投